The acquisitions for this plate

Type: object

root plate acquisitions acquisitions items id
Type: integer

A unique identifier within the context of the plate

root plate acquisitions acquisitions items maximumfieldcount
Type: integer

The maximum number of fields of view for the acquisition

Value must be strictly greater than 0

root plate acquisitions acquisitions items name
Type: string

The name of the acquisition

root plate acquisitions acquisitions items description
Type: string

The description of the acquisition

root plate acquisitions acquisitions items starttime
Type: integer

The start timestamp of the acquisition, expressed as epoch time i.e. the number seconds since the Epoch

Value must be greater or equal to 0

root plate acquisitions acquisitions items endtime
Type: integer

The end timestamp of the acquisition, expressed as epoch time i.e. the number seconds since the Epoch

Value must be greater or equal to 0

Type: integer

Type: array of object

root plate wells wells items columnIndex
